narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I made so much progress in the class and gained better understanding of art
Yea. I would recommend. Super fun. You learn a lot about the artist process and yourself. Great course

Body, Space and Time is an advanced level art course, so a certain level of comfortability with technology/building and the conversations in art critiques is definitely necessary. If you are willing to put in the effort, it is a potentially life-changing course.
